y\",\"intensity\":0.76},{\"key\":\"Quiet vs Chaotic\",\"pole\":\"Quiet\",\"intensity\":0.72},{\"key\":\"Organic Decay vs Clean Sterile\",\"pole\":\"Clean Sterile\",\"intensity\":0.68}],\"prompt_fragments\":[{\"text\":\"glossy parametric-grown towers with visible plasma-seams\",\"weight\":0.76},{\"text\":\"ritual assembly motifs and mythic glyphs\",\"weight\":0.73},{\"text\":\"warm spectral (candlelike) lighting over clean sterile platforms\",\"weight\":0.68},{\"text\":\"quiet elegant terraces, human-scale markets, scarce precious objects\",\"weight\":0.72},{\"text\":\"pockets of organic decay and hand-forged accents\",\"weight\":0.68}],\"raw_profile\":{\"id\":6,\"profile_name\":\"Crater City Overall\",\"created_at\":\"2025-11-03 21:48:26\",\"axes_count\":21}}}}]', NULL, '2025-11-09 23:56:30', '2025-11-28 11:49:16', 1, 1, 9),
